' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_93r')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_93r" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_93r" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/steven0461/">steven0461</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">22 April 2009 01:55:28PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_93r'>8 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_93r'] = ['7 points', '8 points', '9 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_93r')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_93r" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
