<p>Alan Perlis (concerning computer programs, but I think the same is commonly true elsewhere)</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_8dr"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_8dr" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_8dr')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_8dr" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_8dr')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_8dr" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/bs/rationality_quotes_april_2009/8dr?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_8dr" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_8dr')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_8dr class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_8dr" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_8cj" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_8cj" class="parent"><a name="8cj" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_8cj" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_8cj" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_8cj" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/benthamite/">benthamite</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">18 April 2009 09:59:07PM</span><span class="votes " >3 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_8cj'] = ['2 points', '3 points', '4 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_8cj')">[+] (1 child)</a></div><div id="display_t1_8cj" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_8cj" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/benthamite/">benthamite</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">18 April 2009 09:59:07PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_8cj'>3 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_8cj'] = ['2 points', '3 points', '4 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_8cj')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_8cj" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
