points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_884')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_884" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
  <p>We consider ourselves distinguished from the ape by the power of thought. We do not remember that it is like the power of walking in the one-year-old. We think, it is true, but we think so badly that I often feel it would be better if we did not.</p>
</blockquote>

